Title: Strange Dogs
Writer: Daniel Abraham, Mark Fergus, Ty Franck
Actors: Steven Strait, Wes Chatham, Dominique Tipper
Plot: The Rocinante crew make a startling discovery on an asteroid. Avasarala and Bobbie contend with the devastation on Earth. Drummer and her family must make a heartbreaking decision. On Ceres, Marco and Filip's struggles turn inward.
